class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6398989\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6398989\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kdp1710932019987.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kdp1710932019987.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kdp1710932019987.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kdp1710932019987\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">[FORMATTING]</code> section of the assignment file allows you to assign\n\t\trules and customize the code formatting tool in the Source Editor.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__section_w2371ab1b5b1_w2372ab1b5_w2373ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433199e52\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">[FORMATTING]</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><em class=\"ph i\">Rule</em> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <em class=\"ph i\">Value</em></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__section_hgk_gsr_51c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433199e72\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__ul_rk1_qtr_51c\">\n<li class=\"li\">Rule: The rule specification syntax. Refer to the following <strong class=\"ph b\">Code Formatting Rules</strong>\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttable for the list of all possible options.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Value: The value for the specified rule syntax.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__section_ic2_hsr_51c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433199e93\">Example: Setting Rules</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">The following example of the assignment file defines a rule that turns off the variable\n\t\t\t\talignment feature when formatting the ProcScript\n\t\t\t\tcode:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kdp1710932019987_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__codeblock_anh_ytr_51c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[FORMATTING]\nalignVariables = false\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__section_bf2_3sr_51c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433199e104\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">Uniface provides various rules for customizing the behavior of the code formatting tool in the\n\t\t\t\tUniface IDE ProcScript Editors. <div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"5\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__table_mzt_ztr_51c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Code Formatting Rules</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Rule</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Data Type</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Possible Values</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Default Value</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">AlignVariables</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Align the contents of 'variables' blocks into perfect\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcolumns. The columns may contain in the following order:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDatatype and type-specific attributes, Parameter name,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDirection, and Comment (optional).</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true, false</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">AlignParams</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Align the contents of 'params' blocks into perfect columns.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe columns may contain in the  following order: Datatype and\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ttype-specific attributes, Variable name, and Comment\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t(optional).</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true, false</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">IndentVariables</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Add extra indentation to the 'variables' block. By default,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe block's indentation starts from zero. This is only effective\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twhen the block is placed into a trigger, operation, function,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tetc. Component variables are not affected.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true, false</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">false</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">IndentParams</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Add extra indentation to the 'params' block. By default, the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tblock's indentation starts from zero.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true, false</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">false</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">IndentScope</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Add extra indentation to the 'scope' block. By default, the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tblock's indentation starts from zero.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true, false</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">false</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">IndentTabs</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">When true, indentation is performed with tabs. When false,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tindentation is performed with spaces.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true, false</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">true</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">IndentSize</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">integer</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">When using tabs, IndentSize determines the width of a tab.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhen using spaces, IndentSize determines the number of spaces\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthat represent a single tab.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">1, 2, 3, 4, ...</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__note_fbt_d5r_51c\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Boolean types accept all Uniface boolean values,\n\t\t\t\t\tsuch as 0, 1, true, and false.</div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__section_fgv_ktr_51c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d433199e287\">Example: Modifying the IndentParams rule</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">You need to first activate the rule in your ASN file as shown below:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kdp1710932019987_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__codeblock_eyk_2vr_51c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[FORMATTING]\nIndentParams = false \n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Behavior on the code formatting tool</strong></p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__ul_tvf_yrx_51c\">\n<li class=\"li\">Formatted code with the rule\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdisabled:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kdp1710932019987_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__codeblock_jpf_1sx_51c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; Before enabling the rule - Default behavior.\noperation myOper\nparams\n  string myString : OUT\nendparams\n  myString = \"Operation complete.\"\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n<li class=\"li\">Formatted code with the rule\n\t\t\t\t\t\tenabled:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kdp1710932019987_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kdp1710932019987__codeblock_bnb_3vr_51c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; After enabling the rule - Customized behavior.\noperation myOper\n  params\n    string myString : INOUT\n  endparams\n  myString = \"Operation complete.\"\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6398989\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6398989\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[FORMATTING] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [FORMATTING] section of the assignment file allows you to assign rules and customize the code formatting tool in the Source Editor. Syntax [FORMATTING] Rule { = } Value Arguments Rule: The rule specification syntax. Refer to the following Code Formatting Rules table for the list of all possible options. Value: The value for the specified rule syntax. Example: Setting Rules The following example of the assignment file defines a rule that turns off the variable alignment feature when formatting the ProcScript code: Explain this code [FORMATTING] alignVariables = false Copy Description Uniface provides various rules for customizing the behavior of the code formatting tool in the Uniface IDE ProcScript Editors. Table 1. Code Formatting Rules Rule Data Type Description Possible Values Default Value AlignVariables boolean Align the contents of 'variables' blocks into perfect columns. The columns may contain in the following order: Datatype and type-specific attributes, Parameter name, Direction, and Comment (optional). true, false true AlignParams boolean Align the contents of 'params' blocks into perfect columns. The columns may contain in the following order: Datatype and type-specific attributes, Variable name, and Comment (optional). true, false true IndentVariables boolean Add extra indentation to the 'variables' block. By default, the block's indentation starts from zero. This is only effective when the block is placed into a trigger, operation, function, etc. Component variables are not affected. true, false false IndentParams boolean Add extra indentation to the 'params' block. By default, the block's indentation starts from zero. true, false false IndentScope boolean Add extra indentation to the 'scope' block. By default, the block's indentation starts from zero. true, false false IndentTabs boolean When true, indentation is performed with tabs. When false, indentation is performed with spaces. true, false true IndentSize integer When using tabs, IndentSize determines the width of a tab. When using spaces, IndentSize determines the number of spaces that represent a single tab. 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 4 Note: Boolean types accept all Uniface boolean values, such as 0, 1, true, and false. Example: Modifying the IndentParams rule You need to first activate the rule in your ASN file as shown below: Explain this code [FORMATTING] IndentParams = false Copy Behavior on the code formatting tool Formatted code with the rule disabled: Explain this code ; Before enabling the rule - Default behavior. operation myOper params string myString : OUT endparams myString = \"Operation complete.\" end Copy Formatted code with the rule enabled: Explain this code ; After enabling the rule - Customized behavior. operation myOper params string myString : INOUT endparams myString = \"Operation complete.\" end Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}